%h2 Setup

%h3 Requirements

%p 
	See the 
	= link_to "install", "/documentation/getting-started" 
	section.

%h3 Set up The Library

%ol 
	%li 
		:markdown
			Clone the repository:  `git clone git@github.com:krainboltgreene/artoo.git`
	%li 
		:markdown
			Optional Create a gemset: `rvm --create --rvmrc 1.9.3@artoo`
	%li 
		:markdown
			Install all the dependencies: bundle install`

%h3 Tests

%p 
	:markdown
		Make sure the tests pass: `rake test`

